  "description": "The Key Variable Loader (KVL) 5000 PIKE provides security services for the KVL 5000. The KVL 5000 is a portable key distribution device that consists of KVL Host Application processor and KVL 5000 PIKE Hardware Security Module (HSM). The KVL 5000 allows programmers to generate, transport, and load encryption keys, securely and efficiently into secure communication products thereby enabling secure encrypted communications.",
